videos.description: Florida Gulf Coast open up the scoring against Oklahoma State with a posterizing dunk from Zach Johnson.
videos.headline: Dunk City returns in Stillwater

videos.description: Florida Gulf Coast's Brandon Goodwin drains the 3-pointer from about halfcourt to beat the halftime buzzer, as the Eagles trail Oklahoma State 37-26 at the half in the NIT.
videos.headline: FGCU beats the halftime buzzer

videos.description: Oklahoma State's Jeffrey Carroll dishes to Mitchell Soloman for the strong dunk.
videos.headline: Mitchell Soloman with the two-handed slam

videos.description: Florida Gulf Coast's Zach Johnson's 3-pointer looks like it might roll out, but Johnson gets the friendly roll as the Eagles stay with Oklahoma State.
videos.headline: FGCU's Zach Johnson's 3 sits on the rim
